summary: This document contains the Articles of Incorporation for a corporation named Jeepers, Inc., established in the Virgin Islands. It outlines the purposes and powers of the corporation, including engaging in various lawful business activities. The document also mentions the principal office location and the resident agent.

persons.name: Barbara Mignon Weatherly
persons.context: Barbara Mignon Weatherly is identified as the resident agent for the corporation at the specified address in St. Thomas, Virgin Islands.

keyFacts: The document is an Articles of Incorporation for a corporation named Jeepers, Inc.
The corporation is established under the laws of the Virgin Islands.
Barbara Mignon Weatherly is the resident agent for the corporation.
The document outlines various lawful business activities the corporation may engage in.
The principal office of the corporation is located at 41-42 Kongens Gade, St. Thomas, VI.
